ooks-Classics/dp/1590173465/ref=sr_1_1?crid=1EYX558HZNMFU&amp;keywords=the+long+ships+frans+g.+bengtsson&amp;qid=1672941360&amp;qu=eyJxc2MiOiIyLjEwIiwicXNhIjoiMS42NyIsInFzcCI6IjEuODQifQ%3D%3D&amp;sprefix=The+Long+Ships%2Caps%2C136&amp;sr=8-1" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><em>The Long Ships</em></a><em> </em>by Frans Bengtsson</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>See Privacy Policy at <a href="https://art19.com/privacy" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">https://art19.com/privacy</a> and California Privacy Notice at <a href="https://art19.com/privacy#do-not-sell-my-info" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">https://art19.com/privacy#do-not-sell-my-info</a>.</p>]]>
