e don’t live in a perfect world. And the Western world finds it much more convenient to neglect the Uyghur movement.”</p><p>This podcast was edited and produced by Kaiser Kuo and Jason MacRonald.</p><p>See Privacy Policy at <a href="https://art19.com/privacy" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">https://art19.com/privacy</a> and California Privacy Notice at <a href="https://art19.com/privacy#do-not-sell-my-info" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">https://art19.com/privacy#do-not-sell-my-info</a>.</p>]]>
